OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMPs should not bring babies
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Finto Commons chamber,      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Freview says                
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, MPs should not be allowed to bring     
OL,6, their babies into the Commons chamber, 
OL,7, a cross-party committee has said.      
OL,9,FCommons Speaker Sir Lindsay Hoyle asked
OL,10,Fthe Procedure Committee to review the  
OL,11,Frules, after Labour's Stella Creasy was
OL,12,Ftold in November 2021 she could not    
OL,13,Fhave her baby son with her.            
OL,15,FThe review concluded the "long-standing
OL,16,Fpractice" of barring babies from       
OL,17,FCommons debates should remain in place.
OL,19,FBut it said discretion could be        
OL,20,Fexercised, albeit "sparingly".         
